text: "Eight Second Ride" is a 2009 song by country singer Jake Owen and is the second single from his second studio album Easy Does It. It was originally recorded for his debut studio album Startin' with Me and was re-recorded for his second studio album. It went to number 70 in the United States and also went to number 11 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart. ==References== Category:2009 songs Category:Country songs Category:Jake Owen songs
